/* Table: base_yamatoExpressCode */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_yamatoExpressCode (
EID int not null,
expresscode nvarchar(30) null,
isuse int null,
apptime datetime null,
usetime datetime null,
Buyer nvarchar(20) null,
telephone nvarchar(20) null,
constraint PK_BASE_YAMATOEXPRESSCODE primary key (EID)
)
go
